		<title>想帶寵物出門旅行嗎？這五點「實用小技巧」可不容錯過！ </title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/10/15/%e6%83%b3%e5%b8%b6%e5%af%b5%e7%89%a9%e5%87%ba%e9%96%80%e6%97%85%e8%a1%8c%e5%97%8e%ef%bc%9f%e9%80%99%e4%ba%94%e9%bb%9e%e3%80%8c%e5%af%a6%e7%94%a8%e5%b0%8f%e6%8a%80%e5%b7%a7%e3%80%8d%e5%8f%af%e4%b8%8d/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[火報 洪瑜蓉]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 15 Oct 2025 06:21:46 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[新寵]]></category>
